channel.title: Take your server off moparscape serverstatus?
channel.description: I messed up my first server (which i had posted on the serverstatus page), and i want to post my new one, but i can only register one server, and i dont know how to take my server off the list, or if there is a way to get it removed by anyone. any advice would be great.
